<HEADLINE>
<P>
BUMPER STICKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Here at this fancy resort (La Costa in Carlsbad), I've seen two gas-guzzlers 
with "No Offshore Drilling" bumper stickers. I hope to see one that adds the 
words ". . .if your car runs on saltwater." What are my chances? 
</P>
<P>
L. SMYTH, Houston, Tex. 
</P>
</TEXT>
