<DATELINE>
<P>
SHEBOYGAN, Wis. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An explosion of a boiler steam line at the Aldrich Chemical Co. killed two 
maintenance workers early Monday, officials said. The men had been 
investigating a problem with the boiler, an officer said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
